<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= com.env.seo.title %>邮箱认证</title>
    <% include ../parent/static.ejs %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/BH/account/public.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/BH/parent/account_left.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<% include ../parent/top.ejs %>
<div class="personal">
    <div class="personalcon clear">
        <% include ../parent/account_left.ejs %>
        <div class="personalright">
            <div class="percom">
                <form>
                    <h3><a class="active" href="javascript:;">邮箱认证</a><a href="javascript:;"></a></h3>
                    <p class="pertext"><span class="pertexttitle">邮箱：</span><input name="email" type="text"/></p>
                    <a class="percoma rea" style="margin-top: 20px;" href="javascript:;" onclick="ZC_api.validEmail()">认证</a>
                    <div class="perprompt">
                        <ol>
                            <li class="perpromptli"><img src="/img/finance_144.png"><span>温馨提示</span></li>
                            <li>1、 严禁利用充值功能进行信用卡套现、转账、洗钱等行为，一经发现，有权终止该账户使用；</li>
                            <li>2、 请您合理充值，您所充值金额若未购买理财产品申请提现，将按千分之五收取额外提现费用；</li>
                            <li>3、 充值期间，请勿关闭浏览器，待充值成功并返回页面后才能入账；</li>
                            <li>4、 如果充值金额没有及时到账，请联系在线客服。</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
<% include ../parent/bottom.ejs %>
</html>